      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-gru-pro-sns    =    zero
                     go to acc-gru-pro-100.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Forzatura del tasto Pf1                     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "[1] "               to   v-key                  .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * A test su Pf1                               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     acc-gru-pro-300.
       acc-gru-pro-100.
