           move      "FIND"               to   v-pfk (03)             .
           move      "INSR"               to   v-pfk (04)             .
           move      "DO  "               to   v-pfk (05)             .
           perform   cod-mne-zp2-cll-000  thru cod-mne-zp2-cll-999    .
