      *                  * Forzatura del tasto Pf1                     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "[1] "               to   v-key                  .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * A test su Pf1                               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     acc-sgr-pro-300.
       acc-sgr-pro-100.
