      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                not  = "[1] " and
                     v-key                not  = "[2] " and
                     v-key                not  = "[3] " and
                     v-key                not  = "[4] "
                     go to acc-alf-pro-380.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
